Furutama-no-mikoto (布留多摩命) is a goddess in Japanese mythology.<ref>{{Cite web|title=岸和田のむかし話6　轟川・天の川周辺の話・（3）夜疑神社と唐臼（中井） - 岸和田市公式ウェブサイト|url=https://www.city.kishiwada.osaka.jp/soshiki/3/mukashi6-3-yagijinjatokarausu.html|access-date=2023-12-13|website=www.city.kishiwada.osaka.jp}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=振魂尊|url=https://rekichi.net/s/96486790|access-date=2023-12-13|website=れきち|language=ja}}</ref> She is worshipped at {{ill|Yagi Shrine|ja|夜疑神社|simple|User:Immanuelle/Yagi Shrine|fr|Yagi-jinja|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yagi Shrine|qq=}}.<ref>{{Cite web|title=夜疑神社|url=http://www.norichan.jp/jinja/benkyou2/yagi.htm|access-date=2023-12-13|website=www.norichan.jp}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2016-08-18|title=��^�_�Ђ̌�Ր_|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818202730/http://orange.zero.jp/hara.park/saijin.html|access-date=2024-03-23|website=web.archive.org}}</ref> She is the younger sister of {{ill|Toyotama-hime|en|Toyotama-hime|qid=Q2329261|qid=Q2329261|lt=Toyotama-hime|1=Toyotama-hime}}.<ref name=":0">https://web.archive.org/web/20231101120705/https://www.city.kishiwada.osaka.jp/soshiki/3/mukashi6-3-yagijinjatokarausu.html</ref>

The {{ill|Shinsen Shōjiroku|en|Shinsen Shōjiroku|qid=Q1045362|lt=Shinsen Shōjiroku|1=Shinsen Shōjiroku}} says she is the daughter of {{ill|Watatsumi|en|Watatsumi|qid=Q1474187|lt=Watatsumi|1=Watatsumi}} and [[Oyagami|ancestral deity]] of the {{ill|Yagi clan|ja|八木氏|fr|Clan Yagi|simple|User:Immanuelle/Yagi clan|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yagi clan|qq=}}.<ref>右京神別地祇部「八木造」条。</ref>

She is also an ancestor of the [[Yamato no Kuni no Miyatsuko]].<ref>https://archive.ph/wip/BpEjO</ref> 

== As a Hitorigami ==
Furutama is mentioned as a [[Hitorigami]] in the [[Kujiki]].<ref name=":1" />

