== Family tree ==
Many clans may be descendants of Furutama no Mikoto. This includes the {{ill|Owari clan|en|Owari clan|qid=Q11465311|lt=Owari clan|1=Owari clan}} and [[Yamato no Kuni no Miyatsuko]]. This is a subject of debate.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160422190938/http://wwr2.ucom.ne.jp/hetoyc15/keihu/amabe/amabe-k2.htm|access-date=2023-12-13|website=web.archive.org}}</ref>
